{"tid":1834420,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★港珠澳大橋周五起免通行費7天 7座位以下客車免費過橋","createTime":"2020-01-22T11:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T04:43:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"18de096dbabc4d9947f07f3fdd2750e4e99b86ea","tid":1834420,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"運輸署今日(22日)宣布，根據港珠澳大橋管理局通知，由1月24日零時零分至1月30日午夜12時，大橋將一連7日實施小型客車免費通行政策。期間，小型客車經大橋收費站往返珠海或澳門口岸，無需繳付150元人民幣的通行費，而有關車輛行經電子收費車道及人工收費車道的行車安排維持不變。運輸署稱，小型客車是指七座位及以下，包括司機在內的載客車輛，即私家車及出租車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200122/bkn-20200122185305134-0122_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200122%2Fbkn-20200122185305134-0122_00822_001.html&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=2a58a0bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200122/bkn-20200122185305134-0122_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"623e6ec072cd1ac2ba2cc080095a27a546d1a6dd","tid":1834420,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31921116c113c92c16aa37151ad5734a8a74e55","tid":1834420,"uid":207462,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:19:18.000Z","msg":"加強病毒輸送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88e3b7356f385f6d95ed349c4ea78b75ee4